        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>An additional HVAC filter, Code 16WLS, can now be ordered on new HPV models. This additional HVAC
                    filter is located over the air inlet screen on the evaporator module / cab cowl. This filter is in
                    addition to the filter located in the evaporator module.
                </para>
                <specpara>
                    <note>
                        <para>The filter in the evaporator module is an option for certain models.</para>
                    </note>
                </specpara>
                <para>The addition of HVAC filter, Code 16WLS, will extend the life of the evaporator module filter and
                    will prevent debris from entering the evaporator module.
                </para>
                <para>Customers with models built without filter Code 16WLS can have it added by ordering it through
                    their dealer.
                </para>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
